PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 23:56:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-future-of-neurotechnology-sri-sarma-tedxboston</guid></item><item><title>海洋学家西尔维娅·厄尔：“我们正处于被大自然吞噬的边缘”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/oceanographer-sylvia-earle-we-are-on-the-edge-of-being-consumed-by-nature</link><description>领导 100 多次海洋探险的“她的深度”、唐纳德·特朗普错误地撤销捕鱼禁令——以及为什么她在 90 岁高龄仍继续潜水&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/oceanographer-sylvia-earle-we-are-on-the-edge-of-being-consumed-by-nature.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 23:41:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/oceanographer-sylvia-earle-we-are-on-the-edge-of-being-consumed-by-nature</guid></item><item><title>研究显示草酸盐积聚会引发全身炎症和心脏损伤</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/oxalate-buildup-triggers-systemic-inflammation-and-cardiac-damage-study-shows</link><description>患有慢性肾病（CKD）的人死于心血管疾病的风险显着增加。他们还患有慢性炎症，其原因仍然只有部分了解。迄今为止，草酸（草酸盐）主要因其在肾结石形成中的作用而闻名。该分子是一种天然代谢副产物，存在于某些食物中，通常由肾脏通过尿液排出。然而，当肾功能受损时，草酸盐会在体内积聚并促进炎症过程。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/oxalate-buildup-triggers-systemic-inflammation-and-cardiac-damage-study-shows2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 23:26:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/oxalate-buildup-triggers-systemic-inflammation-and-cardiac-damage-study-shows</guid></item><item><title>纳米颗粒可以去除血液中有害的免疫分子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/nanoparticles-could-remove-harmful-immune-molecules-from-blood</link><description>免疫系统是人体抵御感染和伤害的防御网络，有时会变得过于活跃。在这些情况下，它会产生过多的免疫介质、调节免疫反应的遗传物质片段或蛋白质。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nanoparticles-could-remove-harmful-immune-molecules-from-blood2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 23:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/nanoparticles-could-remove-harmful-immune-molecules-from-blood</guid></item></channel></rss>